-- WestLB Bad Bank May Take Over Westimmo, FT Deutschland Reports
-- B y   K a r i n   M a t u s s e k
-- 2012-02-13T06:05:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-13/westlb-bad-bank-may-take-over-westimmo-ft-deutschland-reports.html
WestLB AG (WESTLB) ’s real-estate unit,
Westdeutsche ImmobilienBank, is looking into whether it can be
transferred to the group’s bad bank, after two years of
fruitless attempts to find a buyer, the Financial Times
Deutschland  reported .  Westimmo has hitherto contemplated selling only its credit
portfolio to the bad bank, according to the newspaper.  -- Editor: Alan Purkiss  To contact the reporter on this story:
